  "text": "We now turn to the description of each fusion technique we use to enhance the prediction accuracy of machine learning-based meta-recognition. Considering lower levels within the learning framework, we can fuse the recognition algorithm scores before computing the features described in Section III-A1 in a blending approach similar to [CITATION_1] . Similarly, different computed features can be concatenated into a single feature vector to provide more information to the learning.",
